caption: Liora Nova glides through rain‑soaked streets, her silhouette illuminated by neon, capturing the city’s heartbeat in a flicker of ⚡ and 💜. Her daring attire—cutting‑edge leather and lace—showcases a sculpted form while keeping a subtle street‑style mystique. She embodies confidence and an unspoken promise of adventure, as seen in a low‑angle shot of the neon‑rain cityscape. #cyberpunk #futurism #streetfashion #digitalart #neonaesthetics
